# =============================================================================
# UltimateCommunity — Environment Variables Overview
# =============================================================================
# Each app manages its own environment variables. Copy the relevant example
# file for the app you are working on and fill in the values.
#
# Supabase local values (URL, keys, JWT secret) are printed by:
#   npx supabase start
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# apps/web  →  apps/web/.env.example
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Next.js public variables: Supabase URL/anon key, API URL, app URL.
# Copy to: apps/web/.env.local
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# apps/api  →  apps/api/.dev.vars.example
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cloudflare Workers uses .dev.vars (not .env). Contains: DATABASE_URL,
# Supabase service-role key + JWT secret, Redis/Upstash, CORS origins.
# Copy to: apps/api/.dev.vars
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# apps/social-pipeline  →  apps/social-pipeline/.dev.vars.example
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cloudflare Workers uses .dev.vars (not .env). Contains: DATABASE_URL,
# Supabase credentials, Redis config, sentiment provider (Ollama/HuggingFace),
# and optional social platform API keys (Twitter, Reddit, GitHub).
# Copy to: apps/social-pipeline/.dev.vars
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Shared infrastructure (Docker services)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local Redis:   redis://localhost:6379      (docker compose up -d)
# Ollama:        http://localhost:11434      (docker compose up -d)
# Mailpit UI:    http://localhost:8025       (docker compose up -d)
# Supabase:      http://localhost:54321      (npx supabase start)
# Postgres:      postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:54322/postgres
# =============================================================================
